HOW-TO:
======

To start the application:use the default variables 3 attempts, time limit 3 minutes, log path is /var/log/secure
./monitor.sh

To set the variables by using command line: 2 attempts, time limit 3 minutes, log path is /var/log/secure
./monitor.sh -set 2 3 /var/log/secure

To set the variables by using GUI:
./monitor.sh -gui
